            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-10-15T17:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-07-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="277" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d277">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.U.31.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 3</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>At the end of the paragraph [which] now becomes paragraph 1 add the following
                    paragraph: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>2. No Hungarian national belonging to one of the United Nations shall be
                            prosecuted or ostracised in any way on account of the political views
                            which he held after 4th November, 1918, in so far as such views were not
                            pro-Fascist or pro-Nazi.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
